Visualize NBA data


library(tidyverse)
library(here)

scores <- read_csv(here::here("output/nba_cleaned.csv"), guess_max = 5000)
Parsed with column specification:
cols(
  date = col_date(format = ""),
  visitor = col_character(),
  visitor_pts = col_integer(),
  home = col_character(),
  home_pts = col_integer(),
  link = col_character(),
  ot = col_character(),
  attendance = col_integer(),
  notes = col_character(),
  start_time = col_time(format = ""),
  season = col_double(),
  home_team = col_character(),
  vis_team = col_character(),
  game_id = col_integer(),
  home_game_number = col_integer(),
  vis_game_number = col_integer(),
  playoffs = col_integer()
)
elo <- read_csv(here::here("output/running_elo.csv"), guess_max = 5000)
Parsed with column specification:
cols(
  date = col_date(format = ""),
  team = col_character(),
  elo = col_double(),
  season = col_double()
)

all elos over time


elo %>% 
  mutate(team_season = paste(team, season)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(date, elo, group = team_season)) +
  geom_line(alpha = 0.5)

by season


ggplot(elo, aes(date, elo, group = team)) +
  geom_line(alpha = 0.5) +
  facet_wrap(~season, scales = "free_x")

by team

ggplot(elo, aes(date, elo, group = team)) +
  geom_line(alpha = 0.5) +
  facet_wrap(~team)
